<lb n="0550a16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0550a17" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 743</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0550a18" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說<note n="0550007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忠＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忠＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】<choice cb:resp="CBETA.say"><corr>＊</corr><sic><space quantity="0"/></sic></choice></note><app n="0550007"><lem wit="【大】">忠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>心經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0550a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0550a20" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">東晉<note n="0550008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550008"><lem wit="【大】">天竺三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0550a21" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT17p0550a2101">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550a2104" rend="inline">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。<note n="0550009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（是）＋時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（是）＋時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550009"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是時</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0550a22" ed="T"/>諸菩薩、四輩弟子、天龍鬼神、帝王<note n="0550010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臣＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550010"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人</rdg></app>民，日
<lb n="0550a23" ed="T"/>會聽經。佛右面比丘，名曰目連，神通妙達、智
<lb n="0550a24" ed="T"/>如虛空，隨時變化、權智並行，普<note n="0550011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還＝為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還＝為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550011"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">為</rdg></app>濟眾數
<lb n="0550a25" ed="T"/>如恒沙，諸天稽首靡不師仰。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550a2512" rend="inline">佛告目連：「彼有
<lb n="0550a26" ed="T"/>大國，去斯八千，處在邊境。不覩三尊之至
<lb n="0550a27" ed="T"/>靈、希聞如來、無所著、正真、等<note n="0550012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔正〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔正〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550012"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>覺神妙清化，
<lb n="0550a28" ed="T"/>習於顛倒眾邪之行，以為真諦。王及臣民，奉
<lb n="0550a29" ed="T"/>事梵志等五百人，各有五通，<note n="0550013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔力〕－【宮】</note><app n="0550013"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>能移山<note n="0550014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝駐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝駐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550014"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">駐</rdg></app>
<pb n="0550b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0743.0550b"/>
<lb n="0550b01" ed="T"/>流，分身變化。國有大山，塞民逕路，舉國患之。
<lb n="0550b02" ed="T"/>王以山為民艱難，具向梵志說之。梵志答曰：
<lb n="0550b03" ed="T"/>『吾等自為民除<note n="0550015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">害＝患【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">害＝患【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550015"><lem wit="【大】">害</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">患</rdg></app>，王無慼焉！』即繞山坐，各
<lb n="0550b04" ed="T"/>一其心，以道定力，山起欲移。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b0412" rend="inline">佛告目連：「汝往
<lb n="0550b05" ed="T"/>彼國，現道神化，長度梵志，濟其<note n="0550016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">君＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">君＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550016"><lem wit="【大】">君</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人</rdg></app>民，令遠
<lb n="0550b06" ed="T"/>三塗，永處福堂。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b0607" rend="inline">目連受教，承佛威神，尋路放
<lb n="0550b07" ed="T"/>光遏絕日明，懸處虛空當其山<note n="0550017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巔＝頂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巔＝頂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550017"><lem wit="【大】">巔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">頂</rdg></app>，山為不
<lb n="0550b08" ed="T"/>動。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b0802" rend="inline">梵志驚曰：「此山已起，誰<note n="0550018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迴＝遏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迴＝遏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550018"><lem wit="【大】">迴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">遏</rdg></app>之乎？日又無
<lb n="0550b09" ed="T"/>光，此將有<note n="0550019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝異【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝異【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550019"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">異</rdg></app>！」中有<note n="0550020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＝邪【宮】</note><app n="0550020"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">邪</rdg></app>者，<note n="0550021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＋（道）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＋（道）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550021"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以道</rdg></app>定意觀眾弟
<lb n="0550b10" ed="T"/>子心，誰穢濁者，令山不移？覩見<note n="0550022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝其【宮】</note><app n="0550022"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">其</rdg></app>心，普有
<lb n="0550b11" ed="T"/>道淨，國榮寶色，不穢其心。仰頭觀見，覩一沙
<lb n="0550b12" ed="T"/>門，當其山上。梵志僉曰：「正是瞿曇弟子所為。」
<lb n="0550b13" ed="T"/>梵志呼曰：「王令吾等為民除患，汝抑之為？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b1317" rend="inline">目
<lb n="0550b14" ed="T"/>連答曰：「吾自懸虛，誰抑汝<note n="0550023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔等〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔等〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550023"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>山？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b1413" rend="inline">梵志三<note n="0550024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡＝進【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡＝進【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550024"><lem wit="【大】">盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">進</rdg></app>
<lb n="0550b15" ed="T"/>道力，欲令山移，山<note n="0550025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝又【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入＝又【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550025"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">又</rdg></app>三下，遂成平地。梵志
<lb n="0550b16" ed="T"/>顧相謂曰：「夫有明達、道德深者，即吾等師。」咸
<lb n="0550b17" ed="T"/>興<note n="0550026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">整＝正【三】，政【宮】</note><note n="0550026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">整＝正【宋】【元】【明】，＝政【宮】</note><app n="0550026"><lem wit="【大】">整</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">正</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">政</rdg></app>服，稽首敬白：「願為弟子，示吾極<note n="0550027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聖＝靈【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聖＝靈【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550027"><lem wit="【大】">聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">靈</rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b1716" rend="inline">目
<lb n="0550b18" ed="T"/>連答曰：「汝等欲去<app><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha">暝<note type="cf1">K20n0833_p1167b13</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">瞑</rdg></app>就明者，善！吾有尊師，
<lb n="0550b19" ed="T"/><note n="0550028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">號＋（曰）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">號＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550028"><lem wit="【大】">號</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">號曰</rdg></app>無上正真、天中之天，為一切智。汝等尋吾
<lb n="0550b20" ed="T"/>往至佛所。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b2005" rend="inline"><note n="0550029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸梵志＝梵志答【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸梵志＝梵志答【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550029"><lem wit="【大】">諸梵志</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">梵志答</rdg></app>曰：「佛之導化，寧<note n="0550030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殊＝踰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殊＝踰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550030"><lem wit="【大】">殊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">踰</rdg></app>於師
<lb n="0550b21" ed="T"/>乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b2102" rend="inline">目連曰：「佛以須彌為芥子，吾以芥子為須
<lb n="0550b22" ed="T"/>彌。」歎佛德畢，曰：「汝等尋吾後。」目連接諸梵志，
<lb n="0550b23" ed="T"/>猶若壯士屈伸臂頃，即在佛前，具陳其情，白
<lb n="0550b24" ed="T"/>佛言：「吾承無上正真<note n="0550031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔神勢〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔神勢〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550031"><lem wit="【大】">神勢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>之化，化諸梵志，
<lb n="0550b25" ed="T"/>斯等內外<note n="0550032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】＊</note><note n="0550032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0550032"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>淨，猶若新㲲易可為色。唯願
<lb n="0550b26" ed="T"/><note n="0550033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝天【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝天【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550033"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">天</rdg></app>尊！蕩其微垢，令成真淨。」梵志見佛，心開
<lb n="0550b27" ed="T"/>意喜，皆作沙門。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550b2707" rend="inline">佛<note n="0550034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝告諸比丘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝告諸比丘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550034"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">告諸比丘</rdg></app>：「我為汝曹說經，上語
<lb n="0550b28" ed="T"/>亦善、中語亦善、下語亦善，語中深說度世之
<lb n="0550b29" ed="T"/>道，<note n="0550035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">政＝正【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">政＝正【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550035"><lem wit="【大】">政</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">正</rdg></app>心為本。聽我所言，使後世傳行之。」諸
<pb n="0550c" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0743.0550c"/>
<lb n="0550c01" ed="T"/>比丘皆叉手受教。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550c0108" rend="inline">佛言：「人身<note n="0550036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550036"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>有五賊，牽
<lb n="0550c02" ed="T"/>人入惡道。何等為五：一者色、二者痛<note n="0550037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痒＝癢【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0550037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痒＝癢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0550037"><lem wit="【大】">痒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">癢</rdg></app>、三
<lb n="0550c03" ed="T"/>者思想、四者生死、五者識，是五者，人所常念。」</p>
<lb n="0550c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0550c0401">佛言：「<note n="0550038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＋（身）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人＋（身）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550038"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人身</rdg></app>常為目所欺、為耳所欺、為鼻所欺、
<lb n="0550c05" ed="T"/>為口所欺、<note n="0550039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為身所欺〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為身所欺〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550039"><lem wit="【大】">為身所欺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。目但能見不能<note n="0550040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聞＝聽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞＝聽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550040"><lem wit="【大】">聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聽</rdg></app>；耳
<lb n="0550c06" ed="T"/>但能聞不能見；鼻但能知<note n="0550041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香臭＝臭香【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香臭＝臭香【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550041"><lem wit="【大】">香臭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">臭香</rdg></app>不能<note n="0550042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知味＝聞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">知味＝聞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550042"><lem wit="【大】">知味</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聞</rdg></app>；
<lb n="0550c07" ed="T"/>口但能知味不能知香臭；身<note n="0550043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔體〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔體〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550043"><lem wit="【大】">體</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>但能知寒溫
<lb n="0550c08" ed="T"/>不能知味，<note n="0550044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550044"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五者皆屬心，心為本。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550c0814" rend="inline">佛<note n="0550045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝告【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝告【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550045"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">告</rdg></app>：「諸
<lb n="0550c09" ed="T"/>比丘！欲求道者，當端汝心。人從癡故，隨十二
<lb n="0550c10" ed="T"/>因緣，便有生死。何等為十二<note n="0550046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔因緣〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔因緣〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550046"><lem wit="【大】">因緣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>？一者<note n="0550047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">癡＋（本為）【三】</note><note n="0550047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癡＋（本為）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0550047"><lem wit="【大】">癡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">癡本為</rdg></app>、
<lb n="0550c11" ed="T"/>二者行、三者識、四者名色、五者六入、六者
<lb n="0550c12" ed="T"/><note n="0550048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">栽＝觸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">栽＝觸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550048"><lem wit="【大】">栽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">觸</rdg></app>、七者痛、八者愛、九者<note n="0550049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝取【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝取【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550049"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">取</rdg></app>、十者有、十一
<lb n="0550c13" ed="T"/>者生、十二者死。施行善者，復得為人；施行
<lb n="0550c14" ed="T"/>惡者，入<note n="0550050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地獄＝泥犁【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0550050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">地獄＝泥犁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0550050"><lem wit="【大】">地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥犁</rdg></app>、<note n="0550051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餓鬼＝薜荔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓鬼＝薜荔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550051"><lem wit="【大】">餓鬼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">薜荔</rdg></app>、畜生、鬼神中。佛坐思念
<lb n="0550c15" ed="T"/>人癡故<note n="0550052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（便）＋有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（便）＋有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550052"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">便有</rdg></app>生死。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0550c1507" rend="inline">「何等為癡？本從癡中來，今
<lb n="0550c16" ed="T"/>生為人復癡，心不解、目不開，不知死<note n="0550053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當何趣＝趣何道【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當何趣＝趣何道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550053"><lem wit="【大】">當何
<lb n="0550c17" ed="T"/>趣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">趣何道</rdg></app>？見佛不問、見經不讀、見沙門不承事、不信
<lb n="0550c18" ed="T"/>道德、見父母不敬、不念世間苦、不知<app type="star" corresp="#0550050"><lem wit="【大】">地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥犁</rdg></app>
<lb n="0550c19" ed="T"/>中<note n="0550054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">考＝拷【元】</note><app n="0550054"><lem wit="【大】">考</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">拷</rdg></app>治劇，是名為癡，故有生死不<note n="0550055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止人＝息人生【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">止人＝息人生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550055"><lem wit="【大】">止。人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">息人生</rdg></app>死
<lb n="0550c20" ed="T"/>如呼吸之間，脆不過於人命。人身中有三事
<lb n="0550c21" ed="T"/>身死：識去、心去、意去。是三者，常相追逐。施行
<pb n="0551a" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0743.0551a"/>
<lb n="0551a01" ed="T"/>惡者，入<app type="star" corresp="#0550050"><lem wit="【大】">地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥犁</rdg></app>、<note n="0551001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餓鬼＝禽獸薜荔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓鬼＝禽獸薜荔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551001"><lem wit="【大】">餓鬼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">禽獸薜荔</rdg></app>、畜生、鬼神中；施行善者，
<lb n="0551a02" ed="T"/>三亦相追逐，或生天上、或生人中；墮是五道
<lb n="0551a03" ed="T"/>中者，皆坐心不端故。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0551a0309" rend="inline">佛告諸比丘：「皆當端汝
<lb n="0551a04" ed="T"/>目、端汝耳、端汝鼻、端汝口、端汝身、端汝心、
<lb n="0551a05" ed="T"/>身體皆當斷於土，魂神當不復<note n="0551002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">墮＝入【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">墮＝入【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551002"><lem wit="【大】">墮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">入</rdg></app><note n="0551003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泥犁＋（薛荔）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泥犁＋（薛荔）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551003"><lem wit="【大】">泥犁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥犁薛荔</rdg></app>、畜
<lb n="0551a06" ed="T"/>生、鬼神中。視人家有惡子，為吏所取，皆坐心
<lb n="0551a07" ed="T"/>不端故。人身中有百字，如車有百<note n="0551004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝人【宮】</note><app n="0551004"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">人</rdg></app>。人多
<lb n="0551a08" ed="T"/>貪好怒，不思惟身中事，死<note n="0551005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝墮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入＝墮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551005"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">墮</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0550050"><lem wit="【大】">地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥犁</rdg></app>中，後
<lb n="0551a09" ed="T"/><note n="0551006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悔＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悔＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551006"><lem wit="【大】">悔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悔之</rdg></app>無所復及。我棄國捐<note n="0551007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">轉輪＝遮迦越【三】，遮迦曰【宮】</note><note n="0551007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">轉輪＝遮迦越【宋】【元】【明】，＝遮迦曰【宮】</note><app n="0551007"><lem wit="【大】">轉輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遮迦越</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">遮迦曰</rdg></app>王，憂斷生死，
<lb n="0551a10" ed="T"/>欲<note n="0551008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">度＝使【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">度＝使【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551008"><lem wit="【大】">度</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">使</rdg></app>世間人<note n="0551009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔使〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔使〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551009"><lem wit="【大】">使</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>得<note n="0551010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無為＝泥洹【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無為＝泥洹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551010"><lem wit="【大】">無為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥洹</rdg></app>道，第一精進者，立
<lb n="0551a11" ed="T"/>得阿羅漢；第二精進者，得阿那含；第三精進
<lb n="0551a12" ed="T"/>者，得斯陀含；第四精進者，得須陀洹；雖不能
<lb n="0551a13" ed="T"/>大精進，當持五戒：不殺、不盜、不婬、不<note n="0551011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兩舌＝欺【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩舌＝欺【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551011"><lem wit="【大】">兩舌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">欺</rdg></app>、不
<lb n="0551a14" ed="T"/>飲酒。」</p>
<lb n="0551a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0551a1501">佛言：「人坐起常當思念四事。何等四？一者自
<lb n="0551a16" ed="T"/>觀<note n="0551012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（人）＋身【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（人）＋身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551012"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人身</rdg></app>，觀他人身；二者自觀痛<app type="star" corresp="#0550037"><lem wit="【大】">痒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">癢</rdg></app>，觀他人痛
<lb n="0551a17" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0550037"><lem wit="【大】">痒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">癢</rdg></app>；三者自觀意，觀他人意；四者自觀法，觀
<lb n="0551a18" ed="T"/>他人法。<note n="0551013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">內復欲亂者心＝心小欲亂意【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">內復欲亂者心＝心小欲亂意【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551013"><lem wit="【大】">內復欲亂者，心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心小欲亂意</rdg></app>當自端視<app type="star" corresp="#0551012"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人身</rdg></app>體，<note n="0551014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飢＝飽【三】，胞【宮】</note><note n="0551014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飢＝飽【宋】【元】【明】，＝胞【宮】</note><app n="0551014"><lem wit="【大】">飢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">飽</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">胞</rdg></app>
<lb n="0551a19" ed="T"/>亦極、<note n="0551015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飽＝飢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飽＝飢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551015"><lem wit="【大】">飽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飢</rdg></app>亦極、<note n="0551016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝住【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝住【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551016"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">住</rdg></app>亦極、<note n="0551017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝行【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝行【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551017"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">行</rdg></app>亦極、<note n="0551018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝寒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐＝寒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551018"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">寒</rdg></app>亦極、
<lb n="0551a20" ed="T"/><note n="0551019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寒＝熱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寒＝熱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551019"><lem wit="【大】">寒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">熱</rdg></app>亦極、<note n="0551020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熱＝臥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熱＝臥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551020"><lem wit="【大】">熱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">臥</rdg></app>亦極。臥欲來時，當自驚起，坐端
<lb n="0551a21" ed="T"/>心坐；心不端者，當起立；立不端者，當經行；心
<lb n="0551a22" ed="T"/>儻不端者，當自<note n="0551021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝政【宮】</note><app n="0551021"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">政</rdg></app>。譬如<note n="0551022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（有）＋國【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（有）＋國【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551022"><lem wit="【大】">國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有國</rdg></app>王將兵出鬪，健
<lb n="0551a23" ed="T"/>者在前；既在前<note n="0551023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鄙＝圖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鄙＝圖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551023"><lem wit="【大】">鄙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">圖</rdg></app>復却，<note n="0551024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">適＝退【宋】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551024"><lem wit="【大】">適</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【宮】">退</rdg></app>欲却<note n="0551025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">著＝養【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0551025"><lem wit="【大】">著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">養</rdg></app><note n="0551026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羞〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔羞〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551026"><lem wit="【大】">羞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>後
<lb n="0551a24" ed="T"/>人。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0551a2402" rend="inline">「<note n="0551027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551027"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>比丘！既棄家<note n="0551028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捨＝捐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捨＝捐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551028"><lem wit="【大】">捨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">捐</rdg></app>妻子、剃<note n="0551029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬚髮＝頭鬚【宮】</note><app n="0551029"><lem wit="【大】">鬚髮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">頭鬚</rdg></app>為沙
<lb n="0551a25" ed="T"/>門，雖一世<note n="0551030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔勤〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔勤〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551030"><lem wit="【大】">勤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>苦，後長解脫。<app type="star" corresp="#0550032"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>得道者，內
<lb n="0551a26" ed="T"/><note n="0551031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獨＝自【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獨＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551031"><lem wit="【大】">獨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自</rdg></app><note n="0551032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歡喜＝觀【宮】</note><app n="0551032"><lem wit="【大】">歡喜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">觀</rdg></app>，視妻如<note n="0551033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（視）＋姊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（視）＋姊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551033"><lem wit="【大】">姊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">視姊</rdg></app>弟、視子如知識，無貪
<lb n="0551a27" ed="T"/>愛之心。常當慈哀十方諸天人民、<app type="star" corresp="#0550050"><lem wit="【大】">地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥犁</rdg></app>、<note n="0551034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餓鬼畜生＝禽獸薜荔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓鬼畜生＝禽獸薜荔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551034"><lem wit="【大】">餓
<lb n="0551a28" ed="T"/>鬼、畜生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">禽獸薜荔</rdg></app>、蜎飛蠕動之類，皆使富貴<note n="0551035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安隱度脫＝壽樂【宮】</note><app n="0551035"><lem wit="【大】">安隱度
<lb n="0551a29" ed="T"/>脫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">壽樂</rdg></app>，得<app type="star" corresp="#0551010"><lem wit="【大】">無為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥洹</rdg></app>之道。見<note n="0551036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟲＝𩵾【宋】【宮】，畋【元】【明】</note><note n="0551036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟲＝𩵾【宋】【宮】，＝畋【元】【明】</note><app n="0551036"><lem wit="【大】">蟲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">𩵾</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">畋</rdg></app><note n="0551037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獸＝獵【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獸＝獵【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551037"><lem wit="【大】">獸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">獵</rdg></app>，當以慈<note n="0551038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哀愍傷＝心傷哀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哀愍傷＝心傷哀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551038"><lem wit="【大】">哀愍傷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心傷哀</rdg></app>
<pb n="0551b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0743.0551b"/>
<lb n="0551b01" ed="T"/>之，知生不復癡。能有是意者，常念師恩，事佛
<lb n="0551b02" ed="T"/>如人念父母；如獄中<note n="0551039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（有）＋死【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（有）＋死【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551039"><lem wit="【大】">死</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有死</rdg></app>罪囚，有賢者往請囚
<lb n="0551b03" ed="T"/>出囚。黠慧者常念賢者恩，比丘<app type="star" corresp="#0550032"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>得道者，
<lb n="0551b04" ed="T"/>當念佛，如是念經，當如人念<note n="0551040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲＝飯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551040"><lem wit="【大】">飲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飯</rdg></app>食。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0551b0414" rend="inline">「諸比丘
<lb n="0551b05" ed="T"/>當<note n="0551041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔轉〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔轉〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551041"><lem wit="【大】">轉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>相承事，如弟事兄，中有癡者，當問黠
<lb n="0551b06" ed="T"/>者，展轉相教；問黠者如<app><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha">暝<note type="cf1">K20n0833_p1168b21</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">瞑</rdg></app>中有燈火，無得陰
<lb n="0551b07" ed="T"/>謀作惡、無得諍訟。見金銀當如見<note n="0551042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（糞）＋土【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（糞）＋土【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551042"><lem wit="【大】">土</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">糞土</rdg></app>，無得
<lb n="0551b08" ed="T"/>妄證<note n="0551043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人入＝入人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人入＝入人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551043"><lem wit="【大】">人入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">入人</rdg></app>罪法，<note n="0551044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語言＝言語【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語言＝言語【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551044"><lem wit="【大】">語言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">言語</rdg></app>無得<note n="0551045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔妄〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔妄〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551045"><lem wit="【大】">妄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>中傷人意。不
<lb n="0551b09" ed="T"/><note n="0551046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聞＝見【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞＝見【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551046"><lem wit="【大】">聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見</rdg></app>莫言<app type="star" corresp="#0551046"><lem wit="【大】">聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見</rdg></app>、不<note n="0551047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝聞【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝聞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551047"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聞</rdg></app>莫言<app type="star" corresp="#0551047"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聞</rdg></app>，行道<note n="0551048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（常）＋當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（常）＋當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551048"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">常當</rdg></app>低頭視，
<lb n="0551b10" ed="T"/>地蟲無得蹈殺。無得<note n="0551049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目＝自【元】，〔目〕－【明】</note><app n="0551049"><lem wit="【大】">目</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">自</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>貪人婦女，無得形
<lb n="0551b11" ed="T"/>相人婦女。坐自思惟，去<note n="0551050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貪愛＝愛貪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貪愛＝愛貪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551050"><lem wit="【大】">貪愛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">愛貪</rdg></app>之心，乃得<note n="0551051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551051"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0551b12" ed="T"/>道耳。」</p>
<lb n="0551b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0551b1301">佛告諸比丘：「欲求道者，當<note n="0551052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔端汝心〕－【宮】</note><app n="0551052"><lem wit="【大】">端汝心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，於閑處
<lb n="0551b14" ed="T"/>坐，自呼吸其氣息，知息短長。長息不報，形
<lb n="0551b15" ed="T"/>體亦極；閉氣不息，形體亦極。分別<note n="0551053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（自）＋思惟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（自）＋思惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551053"><lem wit="【大】">思惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自思惟</rdg></app>，形
<lb n="0551b16" ed="T"/>體誰作者？心當<note n="0551054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">視內＝觀外【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">視內＝觀外【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551054"><lem wit="【大】">視內</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">觀外</rdg></app>，亦當觀<note n="0551055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">外＝內【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外＝內【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551055"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">內</rdg></app>。自思惟歡
<lb n="0551b17" ed="T"/>然，與人有異心，當是時不用天下珍寶。心稍
<lb n="0551b18" ed="T"/>欲隨正道，意復小動者，即還自守其意，意即
<lb n="0551b19" ed="T"/>為還。譬如人有鏡，鏡不明<note n="0551056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔則〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔則〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551056"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不見其形，磨
<lb n="0551b20" ed="T"/>去其垢，<note n="0551057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝即【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝即【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551057"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">即</rdg></app>自見<note n="0551058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">形＝譬如【宮】</note><app n="0551058"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">譬如</rdg></app>。人<note n="0551059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔以〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551059"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>去貪婬、<note n="0551060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（去）＋瞋【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（去）＋瞋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551060"><lem wit="【大】">瞋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">去瞋</rdg></app>恚、<note n="0551061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（去）＋愚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（去）＋愚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551061"><lem wit="【大】">愚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">去愚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0551b21" ed="T"/>癡，<note n="0551062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔譬如磨鏡〕－【宮】</note><app n="0551062"><lem wit="【大】">譬如磨鏡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0551063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">端自＝諦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">端自＝諦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551063"><lem wit="【大】">端自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">諦</rdg></app>思惟，天下無堅固，皆
<lb n="0551b22" ed="T"/><note n="0551064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無有＝有無【三】</note><note n="0551064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無有＝有無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0551064"><lem wit="【大】">無有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">有無</rdg></app>常。」</p>
<lb n="0551b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0551b2301">佛告諸比丘：「持心當如四方石，石在中庭，雨
<lb n="0551b24" ed="T"/><note n="0551065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔墮〕－【宮】</note><app n="0551065"><lem wit="【大】">墮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0551066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（亦）＋不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（亦）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551066"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">亦不</rdg></app>能壞、日<app><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha">炙<note type="cf1">K20n0833_p1168c17</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">炎</rdg></app>亦不能<note n="0551067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">消＝銷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">消＝銷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551067"><lem wit="【大】">消</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">銷</rdg></app>、風吹亦不能
<lb n="0551b25" ed="T"/><note n="0551068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">動＝起【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">動＝起【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551068"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">起</rdg></app>，持心當如石。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0551b2507" rend="inline"><note n="0551069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛言〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛言〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551069"><lem wit="【大】">佛言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>：「天下人心，如流水中
<lb n="0551b26" ed="T"/><note n="0551070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551070"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>草木，各自流行，不相顧望。前者亦不顧
<lb n="0551b27" ed="T"/>後，後者亦不顧前，草木流行，各自如故。人心
<lb n="0551b28" ed="T"/>亦如是，一念來、一念去，亦如草木前後不相
<lb n="0551b29" ed="T"/><note n="0551071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顧＝須【宋】</note><app n="0551071"><lem wit="【大】">顧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">須</rdg></app>望。於天上天下無所復樂，寄居天地間，
<pb n="0551c" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0743.0551c"/>
<lb n="0551c01" ed="T"/>棄身不復死。道成乃<note n="0551072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（能）＋知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（能）＋知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551072"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">能知</rdg></app>師恩，見師即承事，
<lb n="0551c02" ed="T"/>不見者思惟其教誡，如孝子念父母。<note n="0551073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意定乃有一心＝如人念飯食道定【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551073" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意定乃有一心＝如人念飯食道定【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551073"><lem wit="【大】">意定乃
<lb n="0551c03" ed="T"/>有一心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">如人念飯食道定</rdg></app>，<note n="0551074" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＋（更）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551074" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＋（更）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551074"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">便更</rdg></app>慈哀天下人民、<note n="0551075" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜎飛蠕動之類坐獨自歎已＝虫蛾六畜坐獨自笑以【宮】</note><app n="0551075"><lem wit="【大】">蜎飛蠕動之類。
<lb n="0551c04" ed="T"/>坐獨自歎已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">虫蛾六畜坐獨自笑以</rdg></app>脫身於天下及五道：一者天道、
<lb n="0551c05" ed="T"/>二者人道、三者畜<note n="0551076" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＋（虫蛾）【宮】</note><app n="0551076"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">生虫蛾</rdg></app>道、四者餓鬼道、五者
<lb n="0551c06" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0550050"><lem wit="【大】">地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥犁</rdg></app>道。<note n="0551077" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已得羅漢道＝為羅漢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551077" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已得羅漢道＝為羅漢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551077"><lem wit="【大】">已得羅漢道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">為羅漢</rdg></app>者，<note n="0551078" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝即【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551078" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝即【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551078"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">即</rdg></app>能飛行<note n="0551079" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">變＝戀【宋】，〔變化〕－【宮】</note><note n="0551079" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔變化〕－【宮】，變＝戀【宋】</note><app n="0551079"><lem wit="【大】">變化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">戀化</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0551c07" ed="T"/>身中<note n="0551080" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔能〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551080" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔能〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551080"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>出水火、<app type="star" corresp="#0551080"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>出無間入無孔，欲離世
<lb n="0551c08" ed="T"/>間，取<app type="star" corresp="#0551010"><lem wit="【大】">無為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">泥洹</rdg></app>去者，即能。」</p>
<lb n="0551c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0551c0901">佛告諸比丘：「道不可不學，經不可不讀。」佛說
<lb n="0551c10" ed="T"/>經已，五百沙門皆得阿羅漢道。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0551c1013" rend="inline">阿難白佛言：
<lb n="0551c11" ed="T"/>「是諸沙門，聞經意解，何其疾也？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0551c1113" rend="inline">佛言：「此諸比
<lb n="0551c12" ed="T"/>丘，前迦葉佛時受誦斯經；中間無佛，隨世因
<lb n="0551c13" ed="T"/>緣廢不復聞，至<note n="0551081" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今）＋吾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551081" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（今）＋吾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551081"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">今吾</rdg></app>為說，聞即得道。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0551c1314" rend="inline">佛說經
<lb n="0551c14" ed="T"/>竟，諸菩薩、四輩弟子、帝王人民、天龍鬼神，
<lb n="0551c15" ed="T"/>無不歡喜，為佛作禮。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0551c16" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title>佛說<app type="star" corresp="#0550007"><lem wit="【大】">忠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>心經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>